data.description: Seller Motivated! $5,000 towards closing cost! Nearly brand new & meticulously updated POOL HOME awaits you! Featuring nice new open floor plan, Updated Electrical that includes a BRAND NEW Electrical Panel, Air Conditioner, Garage Door (2022), Resurfaced Pool (2022) and a Roof from 2015 with plenty of life left on it! Beautifully updated kitchen featuring brand new Kitchen Cabinets, Custom Prep Island, Granite Counter Tops, Whirlpool Range, Microwave & Dishwasher! Your newly updated master bathroom features Subway & Penny Tiles, Custom Glass Shower Surround, Vanity, Kohler & Delta fixtures! All inside areas are newly textured and painted from floor to ceiling, making her smell and feel brand new. Brand new water proof luxury vinyl floors, ceramic tile in bath areas, upgraded light fixtures, brand new Baseboards, Interior Doors, Stylish Door Knobs & Kitchen Hardware shows that there was nothing left untouched. The outside of your home features a beautifully Painted Exterior & Landscaping; making your new home the pride of the neighborhood! Located in a highly desirable area of Deltona with nicely kept homes, minutes to I-4, shopping; centrally located to World Famous Beaches and Theme Parks. Be sure to schedule your showing ASAP, because this one will not last long!
